      <title>刺激政策引发不确定性 中国企业债发行量下降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-31/china-corporate-bond-sales-fall-as-stimulus-brews-uncertainties</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于借贷成本上升和政府刺激计划带来的不确定性，中国企业过去两个月在国内出售的债券数量为 2021 年以来最低。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-31/china-corporate-bond-sales-fall-as-stimulus-brews-uncertainties</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 31 Oct 2024 04:05:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
